rcini=E2=80=99s misdeeds included assigning his agents to track down a pers=
on who was blackmailing Arnault about an alleged mistress, as well as diggi=
ng up dirt on <b>Fran=C3=A7ois Ruffin</b>, an Arnault nemesis and a far-lef=
t member of France=E2=80=99s National Assembly. Ruffin, a founder of the ne=
wspaper <i>Fakir</i>, also produced <i>Merci, Patron! </i>(<i>Thanks, Boss!=
</i>)<i>,</i> a C=C3=A9sar Award-winning documentary
