r when Ruffin and his film crew came to the LVMH offices on April 16, 2013,=
 wearing t-shirts that said, =E2=80=9CI Love Bernard.=E2=80=9D (Apparently,=
 there are mugs, too. How can I procure one?) But=E2=80=94aha!=E2=80=94a re=
corded conversation a month earlier between Squarcini and <b>Karine Billet<=
